•	SERPAPI_KEY — from serpapi.com (free, 250 searches per month)
________________________________________
Free Tier Limits:
•	Gemini API: ~12 fact-checks per day
•	SerpAPI: 250 searches per month (83 fact-checks per month)
•	Render: 750 hours per month (always free for this project)
•	GitHub Pages: unlimited

________________________________________

Known Limitations:
•	First request after 15 minutes of inactivity takes ~50 seconds (Render free tier sleep)
•	Daily Gemini quota limits testing to ~12 fact-checks per day
•	Create a fresh API key before demo if quota is exhausted

